metadata.description:
Year 1984. PORKS live and work at the factories in a society where the government prohibits self-expression and plugs a patch for everyone who tries to do it.

A small group of lucky ones manage to break free of the Evil Pigâ€™s cordon. Being free now they meet members of the resistance, the same former prisoners of farm factories scattered throughout the country, determined to end the brutal dictatorship.

Together they prepare for the final Battle for Freedom of Colors, and Freedom of OINK!
